data.text:
Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)

Ques 1.: Where is Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School located at?

Ans.: The complete address of Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School according to iCBSE is: Moti Nagar New Delhi New Delhi India 110015. You may want to contact the School to confirm the working hours before visiting.

Ques 2.: When was Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School was founded and opened on?

Ans.: This school was founded in the year 1962 and opened on 4/1/1991 12:00:00 AM according to an official source.

Ques 3.: Who is heading Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School as the principal?

Ans.: The school is currently headed by I P Kaur. The principal of the school is m. sc. b. ed qualified and has experience of 8 + 27 years in administration and teaching, respectively.

Ques 4.: Which board is Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School affiliated with?

Ans.: The Bhai Biba Singh Khalsa Sr Sec Sch School is a Senior Secondary School which is affiliated by Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE) from 1/4/2017 to 31/ 3/ 2022 with Provisional affiliation type. Please contact the school for present affiliation status.
